---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Donut Academy" description="AI-Native Crypto Trading Infrastructure — Learn the architecture. Understand the principles. Build the future.">

<!-- Hero + Game Zone -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="game-tabs">
    <div class="game-tab active" data-game="catch">CATCH COINS</div>
    <div class="game-tab" data-game="breakout">BREAKOUT</div>
    <div class="game-tab" data-game="flappy">FLAPPY DONUT</div>
    <div class="game-tab" data-game="puzzle">PIXEL PUZZLE</div>
  </div>
  <div class="game-area">
    <canvas id="gameCanvas"></canvas>
    <div class="game-score" id="gameScore"></div>
    <div class="game-hint" id="gameHint"></div>
    <div class="game-overlay" id="gameOverlay">
      <button class="start-btn" id="startBtn">START</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:20px;text-align:center">
    <h1>DONUT <span>ACADEMY</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">AI-Native Crypto Trading Infrastructure / AI 原生加密交易基础设施</p>
    <p class="tagline">Learn the architecture. Understand the principles. Build the future.</p>
    <div class="hero-pills">
      <span class="hero-pill hl">AI AGENTS</span>
      <span class="hero-pill">TURNKEY SECURED</span>
      <span class="hero-pill">MULTI-EXCHANGE</span>
      <span class="hero-pill hl">AUTH REQUIRED</span>
      <span class="hero-pill">PRIVATE BETA</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- S1: Vision -->
<div class="section" id="vision">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">01</span>
    <span class="section-title">THE D0 THESIS</span>
    <span class="section-sub">D0 核心命题</span>
  </div>

  <div class="thesis-box">
    <p>交易的未来属于 <strong style="color:var(--accent)">AI Agent</strong>，而不是人类点击按钮。</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2)">D0 是专为 AI Agent 原生设计的加密交易 CLI 和执行层。不是给人用的 GUI 加了个 API，而是从第一行代码开始就为 Agent 而生。</p>
    <div class="formula">HUMAN INTENT -> AI UNDERSTANDING -> D0 EXECUTION -> ON-CHAIN SETTLEMENT</div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card accent-purple">
      <div class="card-title">WHY NOW</div>
      <ul>
        <li>LLM 能力突破 — Agent 可以理解复杂交易意图</li>
        <li>链上基础设施成熟 — DEX 流动性+速度可用</li>
        <li>非托管需求激增 — CEX 信任危机后的确定性趋势</li>
        <li>现有工具的缺口 — 缺乏真正 Agent-native 的交易基础设施</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card accent-gold">
      <div class="card-title">D0 DIFFERENTIATOR</div>
      <ul>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--gold)">Login Once</strong> — 一次登录，所有读写操作全覆盖</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--gold)">Agent-First</strong> — CLI 即 API，天然适配 AI 调用</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--gold)">Turnkey Secured</strong> — 云端密钥托管，用户无需管理私钥</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--gold)">Multi-Exchange</strong> — Hyperliquid, Polymarket 等统一接入</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="more-links">
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/agent-economy-thesis/">READ THE FULL THESIS →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- S2: Architecture -->
<div class="section" id="architecture">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">02</span>
    <span class="section-title">AGENT EXECUTION ARCHITECTURE</span>
    <span class="section-sub">Agent 执行架构</span>
  </div>

  <p class="section-desc">D0 的核心架构：将自然语言意图转化为链上执行。每一层都可独立运作，也可由 AI Agent 端到端驱动。</p>

  <div class="arch-flow">
    <div class="arch-node">
      <div class="arch-name">INTENT</div>
      <div class="arch-desc">自然语言输入<br>"Buy 0.1 ETH"</div>
    </div>
    <span class="arch-arrow">-></span>
    <div class="arch-node hl">
      <div class="arch-name">AI PARSE</div>
      <div class="arch-desc">意图识别<br>参数提取</div>
    </div>
    <span class="arch-arrow">-></span>
    <div class="arch-node">
      <div class="arch-name">STRATEGY</div>
      <div class="arch-desc">策略路由<br>风控校验</div>
    </div>
    <span class="arch-arrow">-></span>
    <div class="arch-node hl">
      <div class="arch-name">D0 CLI</div>
      <div class="arch-desc">指令执行<br>签名广播</div>
    </div>
    <span class="arch-arrow">-></span>
    <div class="arch-node">
      <div class="arch-name">ON-CHAIN</div>
      <div class="arch-desc">链上结算<br>状态确认</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-label">Read Layer</div>
      <div class="card-title" style="font-size:16px">DATA ACCESS</div>
      <p>价格、K线、订单簿、持仓、资金费率。<strong style="color:var(--green)">无需私钥</strong>，零配置即可调用。</p>
      <div style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="tag tag-green">NO KEY NEEDED</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-label">Write Layer</div>
      <div class="card-title" style="font-size:16px">EXECUTION</div>
      <p>下单、撤单、平仓、止损。EIP-712 签名，私钥不离开本地，链上验证。</p>
      <div style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">LOCAL SIGNING</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-label">Strategy Layer</div>
      <div class="card-title" style="font-size:16px">AUTOMATION</div>
      <p>网格交易、趋势跟踪、套利策略。Agent 可自主组合策略模块执行。</p>
      <div style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="tag tag-gold">AGENT-DRIVEN</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="more-links">
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/agentic-trading-stack/">READ THE ARCHITECTURE DEEP-DIVE →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- S3: Product Methodology -->
<div class="section" id="methodology">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">03</span>
    <span class="section-title">PRODUCT BREAKTHROUGH METHODOLOGY</span>
    <span class="section-sub">D0 产品突破方法论</span>
  </div>

  <p class="section-desc">D0 的产品设计遵循五条核心原则。每一条都指向同一个目标：<strong style="color:var(--text)">让 AI Agent 成为一等公民</strong>。</p>

  <div class="principle-list">
    <div class="principle-row">
      <span class="principle-num">01</span>
      <div class="principle-body">
        <h4>CLI-as-API / 命令行即接口</h4>
        <p>不是先做 GUI 再包 API，而是 CLI 本身就是标准接口。AI Agent 可以像人类一样直接调用命令行，无需额外 SDK 或封装层。这消除了传统 API 集成的摩擦。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-row">
      <span class="principle-num">02</span>
      <div class="principle-body">
        <h4>Login-Once Progressive Disclosure / 一次登录渐进暴露</h4>
        <p>一次 <code>d0 login</code> 后，读取和执行操作全部开箱即用。研究、行情、持仓、下单，统一入口，无需为每个功能单独配置。首次体验门槛极低。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-row">
      <span class="principle-num">03</span>
      <div class="principle-body">
        <h4>Turnkey Key Management / 云端密钥托管</h4>
        <p>D0 使用 Turnkey 进行密钥管理，用户无需保管私钥。钱包由 Turnkey 安全托管，交易签名在后端完成，用户只需登录账号即可交易，极大降低私钥丢失和泄露风险。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-row">
      <span class="principle-num">04</span>
      <div class="principle-body">
        <h4>Exchange Abstraction / 交易所抽象层</h4>
        <p>Hyperliquid、Polymarket、以及未来的更多协议，通过统一的命令前缀对 Agent 暴露（<code>hl:xxx</code>、<code>perps:xxx</code>）。Agent 无需理解底层协议差异，D0 处理所有语义转换。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-row">
      <span class="principle-num">05</span>
      <div class="principle-body">
        <h4>Composable Skill System / 可组合技能系统</h4>
        <p>D0 可作为 AI 工具链的执行层，与数据分析、新闻抓取等 Skill 自由组合。一个 Agent 可以同时调用 D0 (交易执行) + 数据 Skill + 新闻 Skill，形成完整的自主交易 pipeline。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="more-links">
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/d0-design-principles/">READ THE 5 DESIGN PRINCIPLES →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- S4: AI Frontier -->
<div class="section" id="frontier">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">04</span>
    <span class="section-title">AI FRONTIER PERSPECTIVES</span>
    <span class="section-sub">AI 前沿观点</span>
  </div>

  <p class="section-desc">AI + Crypto 交叉领域正在发生的范式转移，以及 D0 在其中的位置。</p>

  <div class="insight-box">
    <p>"我们相信，<strong style="color:var(--accent)">链上交易的主体将从人类转移到 AI Agent</strong>。谁拥有 Agent 的执行层，谁就拥有链上流量的入口。"</p>
    <div class="insight-src">— D0 THESIS / 2026</div>
  </div>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-top:20px">
    <div class="card accent-purple">
      <div class="card-title">PARADIGM 1: AGENT-TO-AGENT ECONOMY</div>
      <div class="card-label">Agent 经济体</div>
      <p>当 AI Agent 可以自主管理资金和执行交易，Agent 之间将形成新的经济网络。一个 Agent 的套利信号可以直接触发另一个 Agent 的对冲操作。D0 提供这个网络的<strong style="color:var(--text)">交易结算层</strong>。</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">MULTI-AGENT</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">AUTONOMOUS</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">SETTLEMENT</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-purple">
      <div class="card-title">PARADIGM 2: INTENT-CENTRIC EXECUTION</div>
      <div class="card-label">意图驱动执行</div>
      <p>从 "在 Hyperliquid 下一个 ETH-USDC 限价单" 到 "帮我在 ETH 下跌 5% 时抄底"。用户只表达意图，AI 负责路由、时机、分仓、风控。D0 的 CLI 语义设计天然支持意图解析。</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">NLP</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">ROUTING</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">RISK MGMT</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-purple">
      <div class="card-title">PARADIGM 3: REAL-TIME RISK AS FIRST-CLASS</div>
      <div class="card-label">实时风控一等公民</div>
      <p>传统交易系统的风控是附加层。D0 将风控嵌入执行路径 — Agent 每次下单前自动校验仓位、杠杆、止损。风控不是 "可选功能"，而是<strong style="color:var(--text)">执行的前提条件</strong>。</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">EMBEDDED RISK</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">PRE-EXECUTION</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">MS LATENCY</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-purple">
      <div class="card-title">PARADIGM 4: VERIFIABLE STRATEGY TRANSPARENCY</div>
      <div class="card-label">可验证策略透明度</div>
      <p>Agent 的每一笔交易都在链上可验证。策略逻辑开源，执行结果链上可查。这打破了传统 "黑箱量化" 的信任问题 — 你不需要信任 Agent，你只需要验证链上记录。</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">ON-CHAIN PROOF</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">OPEN SOURCE</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">TRUSTLESS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="more-links">
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/agent-to-agent-economy/">PARADIGM 1: AGENT ECONOMY →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/intent-centric-execution/">PARADIGM 2: INTENT EXECUTION →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/realtime-risk-first-class/">PARADIGM 3: REAL-TIME RISK →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/verifiable-transparency/">PARADIGM 4: VERIFIABLE TRANSPARENCY →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- S5: Donut Research -->
<div class="section" id="research">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">05</span>
    <span class="section-title">DONUT RESEARCH</span>
    <span class="section-sub">研究方向</span>
  </div>

  <p class="section-desc">Donut Research 聚焦 AI 交易基础设施的核心问题。以下是当前活跃研究课题。</p>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px">
    <div class="research-card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent)">
      <div class="research-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">ACTIVE</span>
        <span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">DR-001</span>
      </div>
      <h3>AI Agent 交易意图解析的准确率边界</h3>
      <p>研究 LLM 在模糊交易指令下的意图识别准确率。"帮我搞点 ETH" vs "市价买入 0.5 ETH" — 模糊度越高，误执行风险越大。如何设计 confirmation loop 在自主性和安全性之间取得平衡？</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag">INTENT PARSING</span>
        <span class="tag">SAFETY</span>
        <span class="tag">CONFIRMATION UX</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="research-card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent)">
      <div class="research-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-accent">ACTIVE</span>
        <span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">DR-002</span>
      </div>
      <h3>跨协议统一执行语义</h3>
      <p>Hyperliquid (永续合约) 和 Polymarket (预测市场) 的订单语义完全不同。如何定义一套统一的抽象层，让 Agent 无需感知底层差异，同时不丢失协议特有功能？</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag">ABSTRACTION</span>
        <span class="tag">MULTI-PROTOCOL</span>
        <span class="tag">SEMANTIC DESIGN</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="research-card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--gold)">
      <div class="research-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-gold">EXPLORING</span>
        <span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">DR-003</span>
      </div>
      <h3>Agent 自主风控的失效模式分析</h3>
      <p>当市场极端波动时 (黑天鹅)，Agent 的风控逻辑可能因数据延迟、流动性枯竭或级联清算而失效。研究 failsafe 机制：硬性止损 vs 熔断 vs 人工接管触发条件。</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag">RISK CONTROL</span>
        <span class="tag">BLACK SWAN</span>
        <span class="tag">FAILSAFE</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="research-card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--gold)">
      <div class="research-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-gold">EXPLORING</span>
        <span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">DR-004</span>
      </div>
      <h3>多 Agent 协同交易中的博弈均衡</h3>
      <p>当多个 AI Agent 同时使用相同策略 (如资金费率套利) 时，alpha 会快速消失。研究 Agent 间的博弈动态：信息不对称如何被 AI 压缩？策略同质化的均衡点在哪？</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag">GAME THEORY</span>
        <span class="tag">ALPHA DECAY</span>
        <span class="tag">MULTI-AGENT</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="research-card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--gold)">
      <div class="research-meta">
        <span class="tag tag-gold">EXPLORING</span>
        <span style="font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">DR-005</span>
      </div>
      <h3>链上行为指纹与 MM 模式识别</h3>
      <p>做市商 (MM) 的链上行为有可识别的模式 — 阶梯拉盘 (C型)、掩护出货 (E型)。AI 能否从链上数据实时检测 MM 行为模式？准确率和延迟的 trade-off 在哪？</p>
      <div class="research-topics">
        <span class="tag">ON-CHAIN ANALYTICS</span>
        <span class="tag">PATTERN RECOGNITION</span>
        <span class="tag">MM DETECTION</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="more-links">
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/dr-001-intent-parsing/">DR-001: INTENT PARSING →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/dr-002-cross-protocol-semantics/">DR-002: CROSS-PROTOCOL SEMANTICS →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/dr-003-risk-failure-modes/">DR-003: RISK FAILURE MODES →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/dr-004-multi-agent-game-theory/">DR-004: MULTI-AGENT GAME THEORY →</a>
    <a class="more-link" href="/articles/dr-005-mm-pattern-detection/">DR-005: MM PATTERN DETECTION →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- S6: Curriculum -->
<div class="section" id="curriculum">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">06</span>
    <span class="section-title">ACADEMY CURRICULUM</span>
    <span class="section-sub">课程体系</span>
  </div>

  <p class="section-desc">三层内容体系，从基础到前沿，每一层都以 D0 为实战平台。</p>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px">
    <div class="card accent-green">
      <div class="tier-header">
        <span class="tier-badge" style="color:var(--green)">TIER 1</span>
        <div class="tier-info">
          <div class="tier-name">INTRO / 入门</div>
          <div class="tier-freq">WEEKLY UPDATES</div>
        </div>
        <span class="tag tag-green">BEGINNER</span>
      </div>
      <table class="compare-table" style="margin:0">
        <thead><tr><th>Topic</th><th>Description</th><th>D0 Integration</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>加密货币基础</td><td>钱包、链、代币标准、Gas 机制</td><td>D0 读取链上数据实操</td></tr>
          <tr><td>K线与技术分析入门</td><td>均线、RSI、支撑阻力、趋势识别</td><td>D0 实时行情 + K线数据获取</td></tr>
          <tr><td>风险管理基础</td><td>仓位管理、止损设置、风险回报比</td><td>D0 止损/仓位命令实操</td></tr>
          <tr><td>市场情绪分析</td><td>恐贪指数、韩溢价、社交情绪</td><td>D0 数据接口查询</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-gold">
      <div class="tier-header">
        <span class="tier-badge" style="color:var(--gold)">TIER 2</span>
        <div class="tier-info">
          <div class="tier-name">ADVANCED / 进阶</div>
          <div class="tier-freq">BI-WEEKLY</div>
        </div>
        <span class="tag tag-gold">TRADER</span>
      </div>
      <table class="compare-table" style="margin:0">
        <thead><tr><th>Topic</th><th>Description</th><th>D0 Integration</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>量化策略深潜</td><td>网格交易、趋势跟踪、均值回归、套利</td><td>D0 策略模块实盘演示</td></tr>
          <tr><td>合约与资金费率</td><td>永续合约机制、期现差价、funding rate 策略</td><td>D0 Hyperliquid 合约实操</td></tr>
          <tr><td>回测方法论</td><td>历史数据回测框架、过拟合陷阱、Walk-forward</td><td>D0 数据导出 + 本地回测流程</td></tr>
          <tr><td>预测市场</td><td>Polymarket 机制、定价原理、套利机会</td><td>D0 Polymarket 模块实操</td></tr>
